HEADWORD: Ivry
<hw>Ivry</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A battle (1590) in which the Huguenots
under <person>Henry IV.</person> of France defeated the Catholics under
the duke of Mayenne.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> battle of Ivry, Ivry la Bataille.</syn>⟦br⟧
